name: Create Benefit Application by admin UI

elements.name: Setup site, employer, and benefit application

steps.name: a CCA site exists with a benefit market
benefit market catalog exists for draft initial employer with health benefits
there is an employer ABC Widgets
ABC Widgets employer has a staff role

comments.value: # draft_py_date_gt_term_on: 'draft benefit application' effective on is greater than 'termination pending benefit application' terminated on
# draft_py_date_lt_term_on: 'draft benefit application' effective on is less than 'termination pending benefit application' terminated on

steps.name: initial employer ABC Widgets has draft benefit application with terminated on draft_py_effective_on
that a user with a HBX staff role with Super Admin subrole exists and is logged in
the user is on the Employer Index of the Admin Dashboard
the user clicks Action for that Employer
the user has clicked the Create Plan Year button
the user has a valid input for all required fields
the admin clicks SUBMIT
the user will see a Successfully created a draft plan year message
staff role person logged in
ABC Widgets goes to the benefits tab I should see plan year information
the draft application will be created
the existing applications for ABC Widgets will be Canceled
